title: [Maelstrom Bay, Bluff]
description: This bluff overlooks the vast body of water known to the locals as Maelstrom Bay.  Despite the name, the bay is quite beautiful.  The moonlight reflects off the gentle waves lapping up on shore, and local fishermen practice their trade in the plentiful waters.
